title: DDFP 356: Best franchise quarterbacks
itunes:title: DDFP 356: Best franchise quarterbacks
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank to discuss which NFL franchises have the best quarterback collection of all time (19:29). Also, the guys debate if Matt Ryan will make the Hall of Fame (49:13) and a new "shout out" from producer Black Tie.
